20:39.618 --> 20:40.680
Sorry, I've lost the page.

20:50.520 --> 20:53.966
This is awkward, isn't it?

20:53.986 --> 20:54.748
Sorry, I'm OK.

20:54.968 --> 20:58.355
I want you to read it, so I want you to hear what God has spoke to me.

20:59.497 --> 21:01.842
Apparently, I just write too much in my journal.

21:02.306 --> 21:04.890
And that's okay because, you know, the Lord is always speaking.

21:04.930 --> 21:06.252
